-course decisions. | SHOULD | T2 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| MPC-025 | Add end-to-end production-course integration tests. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ No newline at end of file\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-001 | Implement the Event dataclass with score-level, performance-level, reactive-delta, and provenance fields. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-002 | Implement PerformanceIntent per-phrase metadata with arc shape, deviation bounds, tension target, restraint, and call/response role. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-003 | Implement SectionEnvelope with breakpoint functions over tempo_base, density_target, dynamic_plane, brightness, tension_trajectory. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-004 | Define IntentTag enum (build/settle/question/answer/withhold/punctuate) and require every phrase to carry one. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-005 | Define Role enum (ostinato/melody/pad/perc/accent/silence) with grid_locked flag and role-filter policy used by all rules. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-006 | Implement seeded-RNG architecture with per-stage sub-seeds derived from a root seed along a seed_path tuple. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-007 | Refactor composition stage to emit score-tree with PerformanceIntent + SectionEnvelope + IntentTag metadata, deterministic from composition seed. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-008 | Define the OSC/SuperCollider event contract that carries full Event metadata including rule_stack provenance through to the synth. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-009 | Build a deterministic replay harness that reproduces any past performance from (score, composition_seed, interpretation_seed, delta_track). | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-010 | Build a rule-ablation debugger that re-renders a score with selected rules disabled to localize expressive problems. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-011 | Build the RenderPass framework: ordered rule stack with stable order, per-rule enable flags, per-rule quantity k, and role-filter gating. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-012 | Implement R1 Metric Accent: per-beat-position velocity multiplier applied only to non-grid-locked melodic/accent voices. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-013 | Implement R2 Phrase Arch (Todd/KTH): parabolic tempo + loudness arch over each phrase, modulated by section envelope. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-014 | Implement R3 Agogic Accent: lengthen + emphasize notes at local contour apex or harmonic-charge peak. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-015 | Implement R4 Duration Contrast: exaggerate short-vs-long by log(dur_ratio_to_median), melodic roles only, capped at ±10%. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-016 | Implement R5 Final Ritardando: Friberg–Sundberg square-root tempo curve over last 20–30% of cadential phrases. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-017 | Implement R6 Punctuation + Breath: lengthen terminal note at phrase boundary and insert breath silence of breath_after_ms. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-018 | Implement R7 Articulation Shaping: per-note gate-time by style (legato 0.95–1.02, normal 0.7–0.85, staccato 0.3–0.5, staccatissimo 0.15–0.25) with contour adjustments. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-019 | Implement R8 Microtiming Polish: per-note Gaussian jitter σ=3 ms on melodic, 1 ms on ostinato, 0 ms on grid-locked machine voices. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-020 | Enforce role-filter gating across R1–R8 with a single shared contract; verify machine identity preservation end-to-end. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-021 | Integrate partitura for phrase-feature extraction: harmonic_charge, melodic_charge, metric_weight, cadential detection, contour apex. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-022 | Implement R9 Motif Memory: LRU cache of motif hashes with variation menu and return-home decay. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-023 | Implement R10 Silence Budget: per-voice and per-section accumulators enforced at phrase boundaries. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-024 | Implement wind/voice lung-capacity constraints: 4–8 s continuous-play cap per instrument-sim voice. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-025 | Implement R11 Call-Response Gating: follower phrase intent complements leader's realized performance. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-026 | Compose SectionEnvelope with phrase arcs multiplicatively so section-level tempo elasticity modulates phrase-level shaping. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-027 | Implement tempo-dependent swing curve per Friberg/Sundström (3.5:1 at slow tempi down toward 1:1 at fast), with short-note near-constant ~100 ms. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-028 | Add arc-shape variety so not every phrase uses a symmetric parabola: per-phrase random selection from parabolic/cosine/asymmetric-Bezier/flat/inverted with peak-position variance. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-029 | Implement restraint parameter enforced as global dampener across rules. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-030 | Implement R12 Sensor-to-Intent Aggregation Matrix: smoothed IIR + hysteresis → aggregate intentions (global_energy, global_restraint, global_brightness). | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-031 | Implement bounded reactive delta track in scheduler with per-parameter modulation caps. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-032 | Couple narrative engine to SectionEnvelope selection so dramatic arcs drive section choice. | SHOULD | T2 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-033 | Expose aggregate-intention telemetry (global_energy/restraint/brightness) in operator diagnostics, never raw one-to-one mappings. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-034 | Build the metric battery: IOI CoV, velocity σ, DNVR/DNODR, pitch-class entropy H1, Grooving Similarity (GS), tempo autocorrelation ρ₁, LZ76 compression ratio, novelty peaks per phrase, silence-at-phrase-boundaries. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-035 | Build anti-pattern tests: quantization ghosting, dynamic compression, motif ossification, random-as-expression (Ljung-Box), symmetric-arc uncanny, dead-silence failure. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-036 | Implement performance-worm logger: 2D trajectory in tempo–loudness space + convex-hull area computation as CI artifact. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-037 | Integrate metric battery + anti-pattern detectors into CI gate with fail-on-regression policy. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-038 | Build audio-rendered SSM + Foote novelty cross-check via librosa on the actual rendered audio. | SHOULD | T2 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-039 | Embed rule-stack provenance in exported audio metadata (e.g., WAV iXML chunk or sidecar JSON) for listener-review workflow. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-040 | Establish listener-review workflow: weekly rendered pieces tagged with rule-stack provenance, ablation tooling documented for operators, review log template in place. | SHOULD | T2 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ No newline at end of file\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ndiff --git a/sdp/run-log.md b/sdp/run-log.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nin