sdp/verification/t-002@20260416t054258z-verify.md:19:The implementation satisfies the requested spatial/reverb/delay production behavior for phase profiles and tracker scenes. `MixProfile` now supports optional `SpatialProfile` and phase-aware profiles include `stereo_width`, `depth`, `reverb_size`, `reverb_decay_s`, `reverb_damping`, `delay_style`, `delay_send`, and `transition_space`. `build_capstone_cycle()` now passes `phase.name` into `build_mix_profile()`, so phase context is available at runtime composition time. Tracker scenes now merge scene-level defaults for spatial intent and delay send into `automation_defaults`, and section defaults include explicit reverb and spatial routing keys.
